Module chromatynk.chromatynk_g6
Package chromatynk.chromatynk_g6.LYnk

Interface LYnkListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
LYnkBaseListener
public interface LYnkListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by LYnkParser.
